# Project Configuration

## Build System
- Vite for development and production builds
- TypeScript configuration in [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- Tailwind CSS with custom configuration in [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts)
- ESLint for code linting in [eslint.config.js](mdc:eslint.config.js)

## Dependencies
- Core: React 18+, TypeScript, Vite
- UI: shadcn/ui, Tailwind CSS, Radix UI primitives
- Routing: React Router DOM
- State: React Query, React Hook Form
- Icons: Lucide React
- Validation: Zod

## Development Scripts
- `npm run dev` - Start development server
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run lint` - Run ESLint
- `npm run preview` - Preview production build

## File Structure
```
src/
├── components/          # Reusable components
│   ├── ui/             # shadcn/ui components
│   └── *.tsx           # Custom components
├── pages/              # Page components
├── hooks/              # Custom React hooks
├── lib/                # Utility functions
└── *.tsx               # App entry points
```

## Import Aliases
- `@/` points to `src/` directory
- Configured in TypeScript and Vite settings
